{"tid":1841334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"急籲全港戴口罩 延長假期防內地生回校  袁國勇：再不守城變武漢","createTime":"2020-01-25T08:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T19:40:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f554b468723f8940ff49168c997b061d90b147","tid":1841334,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/S7QLPIXC32QPMQQLTOXZPAOLWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2FS7QLPIXC32QPMQQLTOXZPAOLWE%2F&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=f7aa5a96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200125%2FS7QLPIXC32QPMQQLTOXZPAOLWE%2F&h=dfe02065\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200125/S7QLPIXC32QPMQQLTOXZPAOLWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n急籲全港戴口罩 延長假期防內地生回校 <br />\n袁國勇：再不守城變武漢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200125/large/1579887310_cbd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579887310_cbd8.jpg&h=3958e417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎於全國爆發，外國專家估計10日後武漢的感染人數將衝破25萬。美聯社<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n【肺炎大爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫潮危機深不見底，中國政府未見有效控制疫情。港大醫學院微生物學系講座教授袁國勇向醫學界發「通牒」，指目前的港澳可輕易變成另一個武漢，甚至2003年的香港；未來數天是守城的關鍵，應號召「全民口罩」，並延長農曆新年假期以防止內地學生在疫情穩定前返港。英美學者共同研究亦警告，若防疫措施不變，十日後武漢患者將升破25萬人大關，鄰近香港的深圳亦會湧現近300宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n記者：于健民<br />\n<br />\n本報從公立及私家醫生取得袁國勇近日發給醫學界的訊息，當中臚列了八個要點。袁國勇指出，武漢肺炎在家庭成員之間的攻擊率極高（83%），「港澳或其他國際城市可輕易變成另一個武漢，或2003年的香港」。<br />\n<br />\n武漢染疫人數恐破25萬<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港取消內地團九萬人受影響<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇指出，未來數天會是制止帶病毒的內地人悄悄來到港澳的最後機會，「在太遲之前，我們現在就應該號召全民在戶外戴口罩及頻密以精酒洗手」。他亦建議農曆年假應該延長，直至疫情穩定，以防止內地學生帶着病毒回到香港校園。<br />\n<br />\n國際專家亦佐證袁國勇的憂慮。英國Lancaster University、格拉斯哥Medical Research Council-University of Glasgow Centre for Virus Research，以及美國佛羅里達大學等學者共同發表了一份論文指出，要制止武漢肺炎個案上升，必須有效控制72%至75%傳染個案，但學者估計，目前偵測到的患者數量，是實際個案的5.1%。<br />\n<br />\n論文警告，若控制措施不變，估計肺炎將在全國各城市爆發，國際間的病例亦會上升。撰寫報告的專家推算，至下月4日，即10日後，單是武漢的感染人數便會衝破25萬。武漢人口為1,100萬，即是預計每100人就有超過兩人受感染。而大城市如上海、北京及廣州亦會相繼「淪陷」，其中上海估計感染人數超過900人，北京786人。助長疫情的原因之一，是本月中旬開始的全國春運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200125/large/1579887308_aa2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579887308_aa2c.jpg&h=440b03a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n袁國勇<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際專家質疑封城效用<br />\n<br />\n這些推測數字是假設感染個案都是來自人傳人，理由是肺炎源頭的華南海鮮城已關閉，不應再有由動物傳染給人類的個案。專家進一步預測，屆時鄰近中國的多個國家及地區，包括香港、台灣、日本、韓國、泰國，都會因為航空交通而承受最大的輸入疫症風險。<br />\n<br />\n研究預計5.1%的偵測與實際個案比例，是因檢測冠狀病毒的困難，而大部份個案病情也可能較輕微，致使患者沒有求診。雖然中國政府已在武漢實施封城，但論文認為，中斷往返武漢的交通並不能有效制止疫情；即使99%武漢對外交通被堵，感染個案估計也只會比預測減少24.9%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200125/large/1579887309_a640.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579887309_a640.gif&h=03344bf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(社內相)"},{"pid":"784ce3d515dce140e48e863e702ec46baddd4ea6","tid":1841334,"uid":251945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"今次真係mola mola啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d66a1d1f2fc0c21df56fd53c8fa46791679f4f5","tid":1841334,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a05707cae1e0748f7928b15ec2c76c44c50e4bbd","tid":1841334,"uid":59868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"以家又唔封關<br />\n街上都唔係全民口罩<br />\n新年假後成班死都要上去既港豬番黎<br />\n到時就社區大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94745a072b85a9803df54edbd5354c6e604a4c8c","tid":1841334,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"agger!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qE2y8jG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqE2y8jG.jpg&h=6e3002bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入境 海關 航空業</span><br />\n罷工救港，癱瘓關口<br />\n從源頭直接封關！"},{"pid":"ddf8e7d2edfeea71e5dc4932a287ce2dc92b3d58","tid":1841334,"uid":306861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T19:40:47.000Z","msg":"咪撚再買呢啲濕鳩口罩<br />\n支那測過都已經唔合格 <br />\n又點會好得過外國標準<br />\n我懷疑係呢間廠引入嚟<br />\n香港人想死就買呢隻啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8jaCDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8jaCDh.png&h=45958c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFOe4ii.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFOe4ii.png&h=2ac83e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUMwm40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUMwm40.png&h=7d3537ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuR4G40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuR4G40.png&h=1617bf60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfpt8K1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frfpt8K1.png&h=890162dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fui3dbG.